{"tid":2263720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[弱弱一問]除左口罩個樣~~~~","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T10:47:30.000Z","uid":251089,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d945d7f95d5a8f4367442afc76c737538f5036e6","tid":2263720,"uid":251089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:48:39.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無呢種經歷<br />\n<br />\n話說戴左口罩都成9個月，呢9個月都戴住口罩識左唔少人。<br />\n<br />\n通常大家戴住口罩見左幾次，加上聲線，神情，自己就好自然咁腦補左佢口罩下個樣係點。<br />\n<br />\n點知當對方一除罩時，發覺佢個樣同你想像中既佢好唔同，差點仲以為自已認錯左第二個?<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無呢種經驗呢?"},{"pid":"b6b42f09dbeef0309b8ab6e9299631a0cb84134f","tid":2263720,"uid":379629,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:56:02.000Z","msg":"咁有得屌你屌唔屌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03d9c9903454e82698587902b6c5a534fb8cdb8","tid":2263720,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"皮膚差左就真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b255bea1112679c2c83eb9fd01ca5a356891af35","tid":2263720,"uid":44882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"有 唔認得 有啲仲要嚇親我 棚牙哨的原來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7893f80bbf52bacc9db4894e4a959fd272f97b","tid":2263720,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:20:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9929144f61fdb879729bf8868103fa86d5e00278","tid":2263720,"uid":11447,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:21:43.000Z","msg":"其實人地都係咁諗"},{"pid":"67322d07bd71be2893a1f2b670c24c96f5dc2776","tid":2263720,"uid":159074,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:30:34.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n新同事黎<br />\n頭幾日返工著哂熱褲<br />\n纖纖玉手 眼化哂眼妝<br />\n<br />\n但因為疫情<br />\n公司都唔鼓勵同事一齊食飯 加上佢自己帶飯多<br />\n我都有FF下佢係咩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真到前幾日一齊食飯就唔洗再FF了<br />\nFF是美好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be2221b756bab7f4c44bfd3d7d6b95594c0bfd6","tid":2263720,"uid":140726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"10個有八個都係靠口罩加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604270eac6223ae73dba1cf1e8a4543844dd8446","tid":2263720,"uid":251089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be2221b756bab7f4c44bfd3d7d6b95594c0bfd6","tid":2263720,"uid":140726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T06:31:48.000Z","msg":"10個有八個都係靠口罩加分<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:18:47.000Z","msg":"世事都被你看透"},{"pid":"91de0347ff1c8a956c9e62211ed5789e15105e1f","tid":2263720,"uid":251089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T07:24:45.000Z","msg":"其實又唔一定係囡囡<br />\n<br />\n但通常都有落差，是否人腦都傾向會腦補成好的一面?<br />\n<br />\n不過重點係自己覺得原全係同緊另一個人溝通緊，唔係原本戴住面罩的那一個"},{"pid":"abb74b5fe7cdbbfafc5d0159e331b52a77d5a82c","tid":2263720,"uid":251089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T10:47:30.000Z","msg":"除罩後可能有好多人發現自己有面瞎症，認唔番疫情時帶住口罩識嘅人"}]}